The paper proposes a model for relation extraction from unstructured text inputs using graph neural networks (GNNs). This topic falls under the natural language processing (NLP) field, which is typically categorized under cs.CL. The use of GNNs also suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper may also fall under computer vision (cs.CV) as relation extraction can be considered a subtask of visual relationship detection.
